"BlockID: 1170
Call context: bidWithPlugin,_bid
None
REF_165 -> reward.nftKind
TMP_180 = CONVERT REF_165 to uint256
TMP_181 = TMP_180 << 128
TMP_182 = 1 << 255
TMP_183 = TMP_181 | TMP_182
REF_166 -> reward.tokenIndex
TMP_184 = TMP_183 | REF_166
tokenId := TMP_184
TMP_185 = CONVERT this to address
HIGH_LEVEL_CALL, dest:token1155(BlockchainCutiesERC1155Interface), function:safeTransferFrom, arguments:['TMP_185', 'purchaser', 'tokenId', '1', '']  "
